The following steps should be implemented in order, 
1) Open the GitHub Repository called: Turtlebot_Burger 
2) Git clone the Repository and do “catkin_make” 
3) Connect the ESP32 bluetooth to the PC. 
4) Connect the Joystick Arduino USB  
5) Run the following command: sudo rfcomm bind rfcomm0 "Address of Device on Bluetooth"  
6) Run the following commands to launch the Project: 
o export TURTLEBOT3_MODEL=burger 
o roslaunch turtlebot3_project_launch project.launch (The Launch file will launch 
everything)
